reviewText: I mainly bought it for the movie Bio Dome. On it's own it was over $20 but here I got it for way less.

Well I love the movies but PCU skipped. Also it doesn't come like how the picture shows which disappointed me because I was going to just keep one and give the others to my mom. They all come in one case though and that resulted in them being a little scratched.
I was looking for the Bio-Dome DVD and it was over $20! I was happy to find this for under $10 used including shipping!
viva las bio dome... gotta love this movie. pauly shore and steven baldwin are absolute morans and i laughed the whole time
